			<div>
				<h3> 2. Does imresizer.com cost anything? </h3>
				<p id="ans"> No, imresizer.com is free and it always will be. I intend to earn from running advertisement. </p>
			</div>

			<div>
				<h3> 3. Which image formats does imresizer.com accept? </h3>
				<p id="ans"> imresizer.com supports almost all valid image formats including jpg, jpeg, png, gif, bmp, tiff, tif, pdf etc. </p>
			</div>

