			</div>

			<div>
				<h3> 5. What is the maximum file size that I can upload to imresizer.com? </h3>
				<p id="ans"> 10 MB. </p>
			</div>

			<div>
				<h3> 6. Image dimention(width or height) is not perfectly matched, why? </h3>
				<p id="ans"> For digital image dimention is always calculated in pixel. So if you want a photo dimention in mm, cm or inch we first convert it into pixel. In case of it's a fraction we ignore the fractional part. So, for mm, cm or inch dimention is not perfectly matched.  </p>
			</div>

